author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
🎟️ To see Justin Hawkins Rides Again LIVE across the UK, visit: 
https://www.aegpresents.co.uk/event/justin-hawkins-rides-again/

I stopped in Portland whilst on tour with The Darkness, the city in Oregon where Elliott Smith moved to, aged 14, to live with his father. I've been asked many times to listen to Elliott Smith and it seemed like a good opportunity to do just that. It's shameful that I haven't listened to him before. I didn't know where to begin - so please leave a comment about where I should take it from here. 


To see more from JHRA,  join my Patreon here: http://www.patreon.com/jushawk

For Cameo messages: https://www.cameo.com/justinhawkins

🎟️ To see The Darkness on tour in 2026: https://www.thedarknesslive.com/tour-dates/

Get a Justin Hawkins Rides Again T-Shirt & Hoodie here: https://thejawsofvictory
